Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu da sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya ya nuna cewa, duk da cewa matakin ya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da ya faru a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren gaggawa suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye-shiryen karɓar adadin COVID-19 da za a buƙata, musamman a cikin kulawar marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu wani kamuwa da cutar ta ciwon kumburi a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin, sakamakon wani abu da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da sanarwar cewa sabon coronavirus ne wanda yanzu ake kira Coronavirus na 2 wanda ke haifar da cutar huhu mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A halin yanzu, alamun sun nuna cewa kusan 80% na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtukan cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar ba, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na marasa lafiya, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na sauran marasa lafiya ke rashin lafiya kuma suna buƙatar kulawar gaggawa.
Yawan mutuwar asibiti na COVID-19 kusan kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna nazarin jimlar adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma muna kwatanta shi da na lardin Hubei, China.
Muna kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Rashin kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma yaduwar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya tana da tasiri iri ɗaya a cikin ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Jami'in Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin batun Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton ƙididdigar farko na COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ƙididdigar haƙuri ta WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta fara gano mutum uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Tun daga 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU / EEA da Burtaniya (UK), wanda ya ba da rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, daga cikinsu 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Gano yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da kuma yadda ake yada su gaba ɗaya
A Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Yin Rigakafi da Rigakafin Cututtuka (ECDC), an ba da rahoton adadin COVID-19 ta kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka bayar ta hanyar amintattun wurare kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana da karfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don nazarin halin da ake ciki na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
Don nuna halin da ake ciki na COVID-19, mun tattara adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14, don haka muna mai da hankali kan yadda COVID-19 ke yaduwa a cikin al'ada, a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin marasa lafiya a kowace ƙasa tun daga 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na dare idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Matsayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
A cikin jimlar, yawan adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 ya yi daidai da na lardin Hubei, China (Figure 1).
Gabaɗaya a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara tashi a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma yanzu zai tashi zuwa matsakaicin matsayi a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Further Information).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda yawan karuwar yawan kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma a duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya an samu karuwar yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 (Further Information).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris, 8:00, sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun nuna adadin adadin marasa lafiya daidai da na Italiya a cikin makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa yawan mutanen da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 zai karu da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Canjin yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana yaduwa da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya kasance daidai duk da cewa ƙasashe suna da matakan gwaji daban-daban, matakan kiwon lafiya na canzawa, ƙididdigar kamuwa da cuta na iya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa kuma akwai ƙa'idodi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya don gwada COVID-19, gami da gwada waɗanda ba su riga sun yi ba.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa a cikin asibitocin gaggawa kuma jaridu sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitocin gaggawa na waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun karɓi adadin da ba zai iya wucewa ba.
Bayanai game da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti ko asibiti na yanzu suna samuwa a cikin EU / EEA a yanzu kawai 6% da 1% na marasa lafiya (ba a tabbatar da bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara shi a hankali don haɗa bayanai game da marasa lafiya da ake bi a yanzu tare da mai da hankali kan yawan marasa lafiya da aka nuna ta hanyar yawan mutuwar.
Binciken 201011 ya nuna cewa ɗakunan kwanciya da ɗakunan marasa lafiya masu ƙarancin lafiya suna samuwa a Turai a hanyoyi daban-daban, daga gadaje 29,2 a Jamus zuwa 4,2 a cikin mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe suna da mafi yawan kayan aiki ko ƙasa da Italiya (sun sami gadaje masu sauƙi da marasa lafiya 12.5 ga kowane mutane 100,000 a cikin 201011).
