Tun da har yanzu wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da na Burtaniya sun fi yawan marasa lafiya, kuma asibitocin gaggawa suna karɓar mutane daga wani yanki, dole ne a sami bayanan marasa lafiya da asibitocin gaggawa a cikin ƙididdigar yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Misali na Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe na nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren gaggawa dole ne su shirya don magance cutar SARS-CoV-2 wanda zai ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin al'umma yayin da yawan masu cutar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman a cikin kula da marasa lafiya, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka ambata a cikin binciken gaggawa na ECDC na kwanan nan, yana da mahimmanci a yi amfani da gaggawa da kuma gaggawa na gaba ɗaya don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, don haka tsarin rigakafi ya maye gurbin zaman gida, saboda ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da ake tsammani na iya hana masu yanke shawara da masu kula da asibiti isasshen lokaci don nazarin, fahimtar matakan da za a ɗauka da kuma amfani da su yadda ya kamata idan ba a yi aiki da wuri ba.
Binciken gaggawa na al'amuran ya nuna matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a da za a ɗauka don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ƙananan dama ga ƙasashe don ƙara haɓaka matakan da suke ɗauka don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da tasirinsa a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar matsalar yawan marasa lafiya a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar sankara ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya haifar da cutar sankara ta SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kama fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, saboda haka bala'i ne ga mutane.
Kamar sauran kwayoyin cuta, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar sankarar ƙwayar cuta (SARS) ga dubban mutane a cikin 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta hanyar cutar ta hanyar kamuwa da cuta tare da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya.
Amma COVID-19 ba ta da tsanani kuma tana kashe mutane da yawa fiye da SARS duk da cewa tana yaduwa da sauri kuma tana da yawa a cikin manya fiye da matasa kuma tana da tasiri sosai a cikin maza fiye da mata.
Saboda yawan adadin bayanai da aka samu game da wannan sabon cuta, wannan takarda ta yi ƙoƙari ta samar da cikakken bincike mai amfani game da wannan batun da ake ci gaba da bincike.
Muna mai da hankali kan manyan abubuwan da ke haifar da cutar kamar gano cutar, abin da ke haifar da ita, kwayar cutar da ke haifar da ita, yadda ake gano ta, yadda ake bi da ita, yadda ake yaduwa da yadda ake hana ta.
Duk da cewa har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen ganowa da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai haɗari.
Bayan bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020, ya sanya tarihin tunawa ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka ba su umarni su zauna a gida a duk hutun da makonni masu zuwa saboda annobar da sabuwar cutar ta haifar.
Wannan kwayar cuta mai alaƙa da coronavirus (CoV) ta haifar da cutar sankarar cuta mai tsanani (SARS) a cikin 2003; saboda haka Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma yanzu ana kiran cutar ta asali da cutar COVID-19 (COVID-19).
