A cewar wani bincike, masu bincike daga Guangzhou, China, sun ce kwayoyin cuta, dabbobin nono masu dogon baki da ke cin nama da kuma masu amfani da likitoci masu sana'a a kasar Sin, na iya zama farkon masu kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 saboda yanayin kwayoyin halitta na 99% da aka gano a cikin kwayar cuta ta CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Amma, bambancin kashi 1 cikin 100 da aka gani a cikin kwayoyin biyu har yanzu yana da girma; saboda haka ana jiran ƙuduri mai kyau (Fig. 33).
Yawancin alamun cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba a sani ba.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV na iya kasancewa a waje na tsawon awanni 48 a cikin yanayin zafi, har zuwa kwanaki 5 a cikin yanayin zafi na yau da kullun a ƙarƙashin 20 °C da kuma yanayin zafi na 40% zuwa 50%.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samun alamomi iri ɗaya.
An tabbatar da cewa SARS-CoV-2 ba ya jure hasken rana da zafin jiki na 56 °C a cikin minti 30; ether, 75% ethanol, kayan tsabtace jiki tare da corol, persetic acid, corophorum, da sauran kayan shafawa masu narkewa, amma ba corolysidine ba, na iya kashe kwayar cutar yadda ya kamata.
A gaba ɗaya, ba kowa ba ne ke da cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka ba su da wata sanarwa ga sabon kwayar cutar.
Har yanzu babu cikakken bincike game da yadda jikin mutum ke jure SARS-CoV-2.
Saboda haka, muna amfani da binciken da aka yi a baya kawai akan sauran ƙwayoyin cuta na CoV, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Figure (Figure 4).4).
A gaba ɗaya, lokacin da kwayar ta shiga cikin mai kamuwa da cuta, ana fara gano ta ta hanyar kwayar halitta ta hanyar mai rarrabewa mai rarrabewa (PRR) wanda ya ƙunshi masu karɓa kamar C-type regitins, TLR receptor, NLR receptor da RLR receptor.
A hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar tana haifar da zazzabi, kumburi na ƙwayoyin cuta, da kuma gina jiki na I-type (IFN) wanda aka tsara don magance kwayar cutar da ke rage yaduwar kwayar cutar da kuma sake cinye kwayar cutar.
Duk da haka, furotin N na SARS-CoV na iya taimakawa kwayar cutar ta zama mai hana rigakafin jiki.
Ba da daɗewa ba, jikin mutum yana da ƙarfin yaƙi da kwayar.
Kwayoyin T sun ƙunshi CD4+ da CD8+ T wanda ke taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kare lafiyar jiki.
Kwayoyin CD4+ T suna ƙarfafa ƙwayoyin B don gina tsarin rigakafin jiki na ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma CD8+ T yana kashe ƙwayoyin da ke dauke da cutar.
Kwayoyin T masu taimakawa suna samar da sinadarai masu amfani da wuta don taimakawa wajen kare kwayoyin.
Amma CoV na iya lalata aikin T-cell wanda ke haifar da mutuwar T-cell.
Tsarin ruwa na ruwa wanda ya ƙunshi kwayoyin C3a da C5a da kuma tsarin rigakafi na jiki yana da amfani wajen hana kamuwa da cutar.
Alal misali, ƙwayar rigakafi ta mutum daga mai haƙuri da ya warke ta raunana MERS-CoV.
Bugu da ƙari, yawan rigakafin jiki na jiki yana haifar da yawan kwayoyin da ba su da wuri a jiki waɗanda za su iya haifar da lalacewar huhu da sauran gabobin jiki, kuma, a ƙarshe, rashin lafiya, rashin aiki da mutuwa.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2, wadda aka gano a farkon kamuwa da ita, tana yawan kamuwa da tsofaffi masu fama da wasu cututtuka da kuma mata masu juna biyu.
Mutane da yawa da suka kamu da cutar ko kuma suna da rashin lafiya na jiki suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar fiye da sauran.
Matsakaicin kwanakin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin jiki kafin bayyanar cututtuka shine tsakanin 1 zuwa 14 kwanaki, yawanci tsakanin 3 zuwa 7 kwanaki dangane da binciken da aka yi akan marasa lafiya 425 na farko a Wuhan.
Duk da haka, binciken da aka yi a cikin marasa lafiya 1,099 ya nuna cewa lokaci yana daukan kwanaki 3 don bayyanar cututtuka kuma yana faruwa tsakanin kwanaki 0 zuwa 24.
Wani binciken da aka yi kwanan nan, kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, ya nuna cewa lokaci yana daukan kwanaki 4.8 (3,0-7,2) don bayyanar cututtuka bisa ga yawan marasa lafiya 8,866.
