Sau da yawa zafi shine babban alamar COVID-19 ta farko, wanda ba zai iya kasancewa tare da wata alama ba ko kuma ya kasance tare da wasu alamomi kamar hawan jini, wahalar numfashi, ciwon hanci, ciwon hanci, ciwon kai, ciwon hanci, yawan mura, ciwon kirji, ciwon hanci, ciwon hanci, ciwon hanci, ciwon hanci da kuma tsokoki.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami wahalar numfashi ko kuma rashin iskar oxygen a cikin jini bayan mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
Marasa lafiya masu rashin lafiya sun sami matsala mai tsanani na numfashi, low blood pressure, rashin lafiyar jiki da kuma rashin lafiyar jini.
Dole ne a gwada marasa lafiya da zazzabi ko alamun numfashi da zazzabi, ko da ba su da wata matsala ta huhu.
Binciken a cikin sashin marasa lafiya na ƙarshen Disamba na 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan bayyanar cututtuka ya kasance 98% akan wuta, 76% akan tari, 55% akan matsalolin oxygen da 3% akan numfashi; 8% na marasa lafiya sun nemi injin numfashi.
An kawo irin wannan binciken ne a cikin binciken biyu na baya-bayan nan na masu karɓar haihuwa da kuma waɗanda ba su da alamun cutar.
Kamar wannan binciken, binciken da aka gudanar a shekara ta 2012 kan masu kamuwa da cutar ya nuna cewa masu kamuwa da cutar MERS-CoV sun kamu da zazzabi (98%), kumburi (47%) da rashin iskar oxygen (55%) a matsayin manyan alamomi.
Amma kashi 80% na masu cutar sun nemi injin numfashi fiye da waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 kuma yawan mutuwar MERS ya fi na COVID-19.
An kuma lura da ciwon hanci (26%) da ciwon wuya (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, an lura da ƙonewa (99%-100%), ƙonawa (29%-75%), rashin iskar oxygen (40%-42%), tsokoki (20-25%) da ciwon hanci (13-25%) sune manyan alamun cutar a cikin masu haƙuri waɗanda suka nemi injin numfashi na 14%-20%.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, adadin mutuwar COVID-19 ya kai 2% yayin da aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a duniya a kan 66,576.
Kamar yadda yake a cikin cutar, kamuwa da cutar SARS ya kai kashi 10% na kamuwa da cutar 8,096 a watan Nuwamba na 2002.
A cikin MERS, bisa ga binciken da aka yi a watan Yuni na 2012, yawan mutuwar ya kai 37% na marasa lafiya 2,494 da aka tabbatar.
Wani binciken da aka yi a baya ya nuna cewa yawan adadin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (R0) ya kai 6.47, kuma yawan kamuwa da cutar 95% (CI) ya kai 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya kasance tsakanin 2 zuwa 4 kawai.
Ana samun kwatancen SARS-CoV-2 da MERS-CoV da SARA-CoV dangane da alamun bayyanar cututtuka, yawan mutuwa da R0 a cikin tebur Tebur 1.1.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da ƙarfin yaduwa fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma yana kashe mutane da yawa fiye da sauran.
Wannan shine dalilin da ya sa ya fi ƙarfin rigakafin cutar SARS-CoV-2 fiye da na MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Sau da yawa, ana samun masu ba da kyauta a cikin iyali ɗaya ko taro ɗaya ko mota ɗaya kamar jirgin ruwa.
