Dabbobin da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane
Canji da daidaitawa sun haifar da canji a cikin coronavirus (CoVs) na mutum ko dabba, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa CoVs (HCoVs) biyu masu cutar mutum suna haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar mura ta yau da kullun.
Cutar mura mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar mura ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun canza yanayin yadda cutar HCoV ke da tasiri mai tsanani da haɗari ga rayuwa.
Cutar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ta sake haifar da ƙarin maganganun CoVs a cikin kafofin watsa labarai kuma ta ba mu mamaki saboda yanayin da ke da yawa amma ƙarancin yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar idan aka kwatanta da takwaransa SARS-CoV.
HCoV cuta ce ta dabba don haka sanin asalin dabbobi na HCoVs zai taimaka mana.
Yawancin HCoVs sun fito ne daga ƙudan zuma kuma ba su da cututtukan cututtuka.
Ba a san dabbobi da aka riga aka kamu da su ba da wasu HCoVs.
Sanin dabbobi yana da tasiri a kan rigakafin cututtuka da ke kamuwa da mutane.
Binciken hulɗar dabbobi da CoV na iya zama da amfani wajen gano yadda CoV ke kamuwa da cutar a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, za mu ba da taƙaitaccen bayani game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin asalin dabbobi da yadda suka yadu tsakanin jinsuna daban-daban.
Abu mai mahimmanci shine idan muka kwatanta HCoVs daban-daban muna mai da hankali kan yadda kwayar cutar ke canzawa da yadda kwayoyin halitta ke bayyana kansu.
Ana nazarin cutar COVID-19 ta 2019 a wannan sashin.
Bugu da ƙari, an nuna takardun da ake buƙata don kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar tasirin juyin juya halin ƙwayar cuta.
