A cikin tsarin kwayoyin halitta, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa sassan da suka dace.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da manyan kwayoyin halitta guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda ke haifar da sunadarai pp1a da pp1ab masu amfani daban-daban.
Ana kuma samar da furotin 16 da ba su da amfani a kowane wuri, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ORFs na kwayoyin halitta masu kama da juna, ciki har da S, E, M, da kuma nucleoproteins.
Abubuwan da ke cikin kwayoyin cuta da yawa suna da nasaba da kuma tsarin CoVs daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin tsarin furotin, CoVs sun rarraba zuwa nau'i huɗu (alfa-CoV, beta-CoV, gama-CoV da delita-CoV), kuma nau'in beta-CoV shine mafi yawan HCoVs kuma ya rarraba zuwa nau'i huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Bayanai na asali sun nuna cewa tsutsotsi da tsutsotsi sune asalin mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, kuma tsuntsaye sune mafi yawan alƙaluma tare da gamma-CoVs da delita-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun kasance masu yawa kuma wasu daga cikinsu sun zama manyan ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa.
A halin yanzu, an san nau'ikan CoVs (HCoVs) guda bakwai da ke ɗaukar mutane.
Wannan ya ƙunshi HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 waɗanda aka haɗa a cikin alf-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar sankarar cuta mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), cutar sankarar cuta ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 galibi suna haifar da ƙananan alamomi, kamar mura na yau da kullun ko kumburi.
A gefe guda, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano kwanan nan sune ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa, waɗanda ke haifar da cututtukan huhu masu tsanani a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa waɗanda ke da haɗarin ciwon cutar numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da cututtukan huhu.
An gano nau'in farko na HCoV-229E, B814, a cikin hanci na marasa lafiya na mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin haske daga zurfin binciken HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun suna haifar da alamun kamuwa da cuta.
Haka ne, yawancin mutane sun yarda cewa cutar da HCoVs ke haifarwa ba ta da tasiri har zuwa barkewar cutar SARS.
Cutar SARS ta 2003 ta kasance daya daga cikin cututtukan cututtukan da suka fi tsanani a tarihin kwanan nan, tare da mutuwar kusan kashi 10 cikin dari na mutane 8,000.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar mura ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta haifar da cutar da ke yaduwa a yankin Larabawa kuma a wasu lokuta ta yadu zuwa sauran sassan duniya.
Sabon HCoV 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda aka sake suna da SARS-CoV-2, shine tushen cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ta yau, wanda ya kashe mutane 3,120 kuma ya kama sama da 91,000 a ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadin mutane game da yadda duniya za ta kasance a shirye don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai sun fito ne daga tsutsotsi, beraye ko dabbobi.
Akwai hujjoji da yawa da ke nuna cewa HCoVs sun fito ne daga ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma ƙwayoyin cuta suna da ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta amma suna nuna cewa suna da nau'ikan kwayoyin halitta daban-daban.
Cutar COVID-19 ta haifar da manyan matsaloli a fannin kiwon lafiya, ilimi, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a a China da duniya.
Gano asalin HCoVs yana ba da damar fahimtar tarihin halitta, dalilai da shingen tseren.
Wannan na iya taimakawa ko sauƙaƙe aikin gano dabbobi masu cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda ya riga ya kamu da cutar, wanda ya haifar da yaduwar cutar, wanda zai iya haifar da tasiri mai yawa wajen hana yaduwar ta nan gaba.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu ba da taƙaitaccen bayani game da asalin HCoVs a cikin dabbobi, yadda suke yaduwa tsakanin jinsuna daban-daban da kuma hanyoyin da suke haifar da cututtuka.
Musamman, muna nunawa da kuma nazarin furcin da aka saba cewa ƙwayoyin cuta masu haifar da HCoVs ba su haifar da cututtukan dabbobi ba amma suna haifar da cututtukan da aka kamu da su a cikin mutum ko sabon dabba bayan sun bazu zuwa nau'ikan daban.
Muna nazarin yanayin HCoVs inda yawan yaduwar yana yawan kasancewa tare da raguwar yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
A cikin wannan sashin muna kuma nazarin sakamakon cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta yau.
CoVs sun kama dabbobi da aka sani tun daga ƙarshen 1930s.
Kafin a fara gano wani nau'in asalin HCoV-229E, B814, a cikin hanci na masu cutar mura na yau da kullun, an gano nau'ikan CoVs daban-daban daga dabbobi masu kamuwa da cutar daban-daban, kamar namomin kaza, beraye, shanu, aladu, cats da karnuka.
A cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
