Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idojin gwajin COVID-19  masu cutar da ake zargi  da waɗanda aka tabbatar da cutar 
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta ba da sanarwar gaggawa ta jagororin da suka haɗa da shawarwari don ganowa da magance sabon kamuwa da cutar coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV), kuma jagororin sun ba mu ƙwarewa da ingantaccen bayani game da yaƙin cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, kuma ra'ayoyinmu da iliminmu game da ita suna haɓaka a hankali dangane da bincike da ayyukan likita; saboda haka ana ci gaba da sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wata shawara game da ƙa'idodinmu kuma mun gabatar da sababbin ka'idoji don kimantawa masu da'awar cutar da masu da'awar cutar bisa ga sabon jagorar bincike da magani na COVID-19 (mataki na bakwai) da kwamitin kula da lafiyar jama'ar kasar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da annoba, wanda yanzu ana kiransa cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an kira cutar cutar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya.
Don magance kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta kafa ƙa'idodin gaggawa na gaggawa kuma an sanar da su a kan layi a cikin binciken likita na Sojoji a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Tun lokacin da aka wallafa shi, mutane da yawa sun ji daɗin wannan littafin.
Amma yana da mahimmanci a fahimci cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, tunaninmu da iliminmu suna ci gaba da haɓaka a hankali dangane da bincike da ayyukan likita; saboda haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani.
Misali, Jagorar Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya bayar tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, ya wallafa littattafai bakwai tare da wasu canje-canje masu mahimmanci.
Yanzu kuma tsarinmu ya karɓi shawarar Zhou da sauransu, waɗanda suka ƙirƙiri tsarin da ya fi sauƙi don ba da maki bisa ga kwarewar likitanci.
Ayyukan su sun kara sabbin alamomi masu amfani da ke nuna yanayinmu kuma suna ba da bayanai masu amfani game da wannan annoba mai barazanar duniya.
Muna tallafa musu kuma muna godiya da aikinsu.
Duk da haka, ana buƙatar sabunta ayyukan su daidai da sabon jagororin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (Gwaji na bakwai) da kuma sabon bincike.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a littafin na bakwai (3 ga Maris, 2020) don tabbatar da cewa wanda ake zargi da cutar dole ne ya haɗu da ɗayan alamun tarihin cutar da alamun cutar biyu don cikakken bincike, ko kuma dole ne ya haɗu da alamun cutar uku idan tarihin cutar bai bayyana ba:
Tarihin annobar: (1) Akwai tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewaye da ita, ko kuma wasu mutane da suka kamu da COVID-19 sun bayyana a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) akwai haɗuwa da masu kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 (tare da alamun ƙwayoyin cuta na nucleic acid); (3) akwai haɗuwa da marasa lafiya da ke da ƙonewa ko alamun numfashi daga Wuhan da kewaye da ita, ko kuma akwai COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) akwai haɗuwa da marasa lafiya na gida (mafi da 2 marasa lafiya da ke da ƙonewa ko alamun numfashi da aka nuna a cikin makonni 2 a cikin jirgin ruwa, gida, ofis, makaranta, da sauran wurare).
Alamun cutar: (1) wuta ko alamun rashin numfashi; (2) tare da alamun kamuwa da COVID-19; (3) jimlar adadin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayo.
Ana buƙatar tantance mai cutar da aka tabbatar da shi bisa zargin kamuwa da cutar da ke nuna ɗayan alamun cutar ko na jini masu zuwa: (1) wani samfurin PCR na ainihi wanda ya nuna cutar SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin manyan sassan kwayar cutar da ke nuna alaƙa da sabon coronavirus da aka sani; (3) nuna rashin lafiya ga ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na IgM da IgG ga SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin jini; ko kuma karuwar ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na SARS-CoV-2 daga marasa lafiya zuwa bar, ko kuma fiye da sau 4 a cikin sashin murmurewa na cutar mai tsanani.
Mun lura cewa an ɗauki matakan numfashi na nucleic acid ko samfurin jini lokacin da aka ƙara su zuwa na biyu (18 ga Janairu 2020) da na uku (22 ga Janairu 2020).
Gano cutar a cikin gwajin jini na jini an ƙara shi a cikin littattafan da aka buga na huɗu (27 Janairu 2020) da na biyar (8 Fabrairu 2020); sannan an ƙara alamun jini zuwa littafin da aka buga na bakwai.
Waɗannan canje-canjen sun dogara ne akan ci gaba da bincike na masu bincike don neman ingantaccen hanyar gano acid na nucleic don saurin bincike, da kuma samfurin numfashi wanda ya haɗa da samfurin jini, wanda ke ba da damar samar da nau'ikan samfurori daban-daban, kuma yana tallafawa samar da ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman a cikin ƙa'idodin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai alamun da ke nuna cewa muna bukatar mu yi hankali da marasa lafiya da ba su da alamun cutar.
Saboda haka, dole ne a sake duba jadawalin Zhou da sauransu, kamar yadda suka rarraba mutumin da ba shi da alamun cutar a matsayin "ƙananan haɗari".
Hakanan dole ne a bincika tsarin ƙimar a cikin sauran ayyukan likita da bincike.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin tabbaci na kai tsaye zai bayyana kuma muna tambayar masu karatu su ba da ra'ayinsu.
Game da binciken "masu zargin rashin lafiya" da "masu tabbatar da rashin lafiya", muna roƙon ku ku bi da kuma bin sababbin ƙa'idodin ƙasashensu.
