Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton mutuwar mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19, wanda ya fi girma a cikin rana ɗaya
Jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da cewa mutane biyar sun mutu sakamakon COVID-19 a wannan ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutuwar da aka yi a rana guda da cutar.
