Sakamakon binciken ya nuna cewa duk 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal da kuma sojojin da ke cikin ayyukan agaji, a matsayin kariya, an ci gaba da duba su kuma an killace su na kwanaki 14 a cikin gidan The Ranch Resort.
