A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen kasar Sin ta ce kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da tallafi zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban jami'o'i na kasar Sin da ke Amurka sun hada kai wajen taimakawa wajen tura tallafi zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa a kasar Sin, inda wani babban rukuni a Chicago ya tattara kimanin 50,000 na N95 don a ba da su ga asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Hukumar agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da haɗin gwiwar FedEx, ta aika da 200 000 na masks da sauran kayan kariya, gami da takalma da sutura, waɗanda aka kai su a cikin jirgin sama na musamman zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun ba da sanarwar cewa sun ba da kyautar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa bincike kan allurar rigakafi da kuma kare "masu haɗarin haɗari a Afirka da Asiya".
Gidan talabijin na Interaction ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da takunkumi 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya tura takunkumi miliyan 3,16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar Red Cross ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura tallafin dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da takunkumi miliyan 1 ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta ba da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta ba da ƙarin tan na kayan aikin likita ga Wuhan, Malaysia ta ba da sanarwar bayar da takunkumi miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da takunkumi daban-daban na kayan aikin likita ciki har da takunkumi 10,000 na rigakafi na musamman kuma Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin bayar da ƙarin dala miliyan 100 don tallafawa tattalin arzikin sauran ƙasashen da suka sha wahala daga cutar.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da kwararru don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance cutar coronavirus.
Jack Ma ya tura kayan aikin bincike miliyan 1.1 da masks miliyan 6 da kuma tufafi 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don yada su ga kungiyar tarayyar Afrika.
Daga baya, ya tura kayan bincike 5,000 zuwa Panama, masks 100,000, da kuma na'urori masu numfashi 5.
Ma kuma ta ba Kanada kayan aikin likita. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwa game da masks da kayan aikin bincike na asibiti da aka yi a China.
Misali, Spain ta dakatar da amfani da na'urori masu gano cutar coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi a China da ke da inganci na 30%, yayin da Netherlands ta cire masks 600,000 da aka yi a China daga kasuwa saboda sun zama masu lahani.
Belgium ta cire masks 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wanda ake zargin ya fito ne daga China, amma a gaskiya daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ta bayar a wasu sassan Kudancin Amirka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da ayyukan gaggawa na gaggawa a kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yaba da ayyukan da shugabannin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafawa da hana annobar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ce akwai bambanci tsakanin annobar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi jami'an kasar Sin da ɓoyewa da kuma hana matakan hanawa da kuma hanawa, da annobar yanzu inda gwamnati "ta samar da bayanai masu inganci don ba da tabbacin tashin hankali kafin hutun Sabuwar Shekara".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, bayan babban hukuma ta yanke shawarar aiwatar da dokar hana amfani da kayan masarufi a Wuhan, babban wakilin Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya Gauden Galea ya ce duk da cewa "ba shawarar WHO ba ce", hakan ma "babban tabbaci ne na sha'awar hana cutar a halin da ta kasance mafi muni" kuma ya kira ta "ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da cewa mutane suna kamuwa da cutar a wajen kasar Sin kuma yawan kamuwa da cutar na ci gaba da ƙaruwa a ƙasashe, Hukumar ta Duniya ta bayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta gaggawa a matsayin matsalar lafiyar duniya kamar ta MICP, wanda aka kama da cutar ta shida a duniya a shekarar 2009.
Babban daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce, PHEIC na da nasaba da hadarin yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman a kasashe masu talauci da kasashe masu tasowa ba tare da cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya masu karfi ba.
Game da aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga, Tedros ya ce "babu bukatar a yi wasu matakan da ba su da muhimmanci da za su hana zirga-zirgar mutane da kasuwanci" kuma "WHO ba ta bukatar a yi dokar hana zirga-zirga da zirga-zirga".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta bukaci kasashe su ba da tallafin dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa matakan da za a dauka na shirya cutar a kasashe masu talauci, ta ce yana da gaggawa a tallafa wa kasashen da "suke da shirye-shiryen gano wadanda suka kamu da cutar, ko da sun bayyana".
Tedros ya kuma bayyana cewa "duk muna iya kasancewa da ƙarfi kamar rashin ƙarfi" kuma ya bukaci ƙasashe "su saka hannun jari a yau ko su biya ƙarin daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, a wata hira da manema labarai, WHO ta amince da COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya sanar da cewa Sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince ya ba da "dukan ƙarfin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya wajen neman amsar".
Saboda haka, an kafa Ƙungiyar Kula da Matsalar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wadda ta haɗa dukkan ayyukan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wadda Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta ce za ta "mai da hankali sosai ga taimakon kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran sassan za su iya ba da kwarewarsu wajen magance tasirin zamantakewar al'umma, tattalin arziki, da ci gaban duniya na annobar".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kafa wata kungiya ta WHO da ke jagorantar kasar Sin don zaɓar kwararrun masana na duniya da na WHO da aka tura zuwa China don taimakawa wajen sarrafawa da sarrafa yaduwar cutar" tare da gudanar da horo da shawarwari tare da manyan hukumomin kasar da kuma ziyartar wurare daban-daban don nazarin "matsayin da ayyukan yaki da cutar za su iya yi a larduna da yankuna da yankuna da garuruwa". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sanarwar cewa "duniya ta kamata ta dauki mataki don shirya don magance cutar", ta sanar da cewa duk da cewa an riga an fara cutar coronavirus, dole ne "kasashen duniya su shirya don cutar".
Don magance ci gaban annobar a Iran, WHO ta tura wani rukuni na hadin gwiwa don duba halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a ɗaga gwajin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus a duniya daga matakin "babba" zuwa matakin "babba", matakin gargadi da kimantawa na tasiri.
Mike Ryan, shugaban ayyukan agaji na WHO, ya yi gargadin cewa "Wannan misali ne na gaskiya ga kowace ƙasa a duniya: Ku farka.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana gabatowa kuma dole ne ku kasance a shirye", in ji shi, yana mai jaddada cewa tsauraran matakai na magance ta na iya taimakawa wajen hana "hadarin da take haifarwa".
Ryan ya kara da cewa, ba a taba samun bayanai da suka sa hukumar kiwon lafiya ta duniya ta bayyana cewa cutar ta zama babbar annoba ba, yana mai cewa sanarwar za ta nuna cewa "a gaskiya mun yi imani cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, WHO ta ayyana coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Babban daraktan ya bayyana cewa WHO "ta damu sosai game da karuwar gaggawa da rashin daukar matakan". WHO ta yi ta sukar abin da ya zama kamar rashin tsauraran matakan hana cutar, kamar sanarwar da ke magana game da bala'in lafiyar jama'a da kuma sanya cutar cikin cututtukan cututtuka.
Wani takaddama da aka yi ya hada da bukatar da aka yi na cewa Babban Daraktan WHO, Tedros Adhanom ya mika wuya, har zuwa 6 ga watan Afrilu, wanda ya riga ya samu amincewar mutane 733,000.
