Maurizio Massari, jakadan Italiya a Tarayyar Turai ya ce: "China ce kaɗai ta taimaka wa Italiya.
Wannan ba alama ce mai kyau na haɗin kai na Turai ba".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan tattaunawa ta waya da Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya rundunar sojin Rasha don aika da sojoji na likitoci, motocin kashe kwayoyin cuta, da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
