A farkon, mutanen Koriya ta Kudu sun sami rashin fahimta game da halin Shugaba Moon Jae-in game da batun.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan bukatar cire Moon daga mulki saboda zargin da ake yi da rashin nasarar gwamnati wajen magance cutar, ko kuma sun yaba da yadda ta amsa.
