A2 (ACE2) shine furotin da ke aiki da ƙwayoyin cuta na waje (kwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta) na huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana daidaita aikin furotin mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang(1-7) zuwa ingantaccen magani don maganin cututtukan zuciya.ACE2 kuma yana taimakawa wajen shiga cikin kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta coronaviruses.
An fi kiran fasalin ɗan adam na furotin mai gina jiki hACE2.
Protein mai aiki na angiotensin-con 2 shine zinc wanda ke dauke da metalloenzyme wanda ke cikin endothelial surface da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da N-terminal na peptidase M2 da kuma C-terminal collectrin na daukar kwayoyin acid daga kwakwalwa.
ACE2 wani nau'in furotin ne mai nau'i ɗaya na nau'i I, wanda ke da wani ɓangare na furotin mai aiki wanda ke aiki a saman ƙwayoyin cuta da sauran ƙwayoyin halitta.
A cikin ƙwayoyin halitta, an cire wani ɓangare na ACE2 daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ya shiga cikin wani furotin mai ƙwayoyin cuta wanda ake kira sheddase, kuma furotin mai ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta ya shiga cikin hanyar ƙwayoyin cuta sannan ya fita cikin kwayar cuta.
ACE2 yana samuwa a cikin kwayoyin halitta da yawa: ACE2 yana aiki ne don ƙwayoyin halitta da yawa na ƙwayoyin cuta na nau'in II na jijiyoyin huhu, ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin jini da jijiyoyin jini da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jiki na ƙananan sassan jiki.
Ana samun ma'anar ACE2 mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa, a cikin striatum, a cikin hypothalamus, da kuma a cikin kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shine daidaita daidaitattun matakan ACE.
ACE na jini na angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II yana haifar da ƙananan jijiyoyin jini da rage karfin jini.
ACE2 kuma yana samar da phenylalanine na amino acid carboxyl-terminal a cikin angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) da hydrolyses a cikin angiotensin wanda ke haifar da manyan huhu masu ɗaukar jini (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
Hakanan ACE2 na iya raba peptides kamar [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 yana taimakawa wajen karɓar amino acid mai aiki wanda ke haifar da SLC6A19 kuma yana taka rawa wajen cututtukan Hartnup da ke haifar da ƙwayar cuta.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki azaman babban hanyar shiga cikin kwayar halitta don samar da wasu coronaviruses, wato HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus mai haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (virus mai haifar da COVID-19).
